{
  "stem": "17761.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I wasn't so good in shooting in the goals.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And that was a very-- when we had time, we used to go and play soccer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was a-- a stadium in our place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And during the summer, there were football teams-- we call that football, you call it here soccer-- football teams who came to play there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we used even to-- to run away from the cheder in order to watch the match, but that's a different story.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That is-- so the life was totally different.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Another thing, we had there two youth movements, one which was [NON-ENGLISH], and the other one which was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we-- it started for me as the first, but I was a child at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We started a religious youth movement, [NON-ENGLISH], who became a steady youth movement in that place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With that, first of all, I was a member.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the [? weirdest ?] thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, this was organized in the late '30s by the man who became later on my brother-in-law, Reuven Feuerstein.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was at that time a guy of 18-something years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was already the older one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was at that time 11 and 1/2 or 12 or something like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he mobilized me, as well as together with other children, and we founded the [NON-ENGLISH] movement and we kept to this even during the concentration camps and later on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is, by the way, very interesting thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My grand-- my father [NON-ENGLISH] was a good friend with the general who was the commander of the city, because they used to go together to the shvitz [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know you call that to the sauna.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The sauna.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we called it shvitz [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
